This is a list of contestants who have appeared on the American television series, ''[[The Amazing Race (U.S. TV series)|The Amazing Race]]''. Contestants with a pre-existing relationship form a team and race around the world against other teams to claim a grand prize of 1 million [[United States dollar|USD]]. The original American series premiered in 2001; as of 2014, there have been 25 seasons aired with locations spanning all six inhabited continents. In total, 510 contestants have appeared in the series, with 22 of them competing again on ''[[The Amazing Race 11|The Amazing Race 11: All-Stars]]'' in 2007, another 22 competing again on ''[[The Amazing Race 18|The Amazing Race 18: Unfinished Business]]'' and another 22 also competing on ''[[The Amazing Race 24|The Amazing Race 24: All-Stars]]''. The series also aired a special season on ''[[The Amazing Race 8|The Amazing Race 8: Family Edition]]'' that contained 10 teams of four family members, including children as young as 8, while season 29 features 22 contestants who were all complete strangers.

==Contestants==
The presented information was accurate at the time of filming.

